"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-26-IOC-s-Bach-praises-CMG-s-preparations-for-Olympic-coverage-1vxYI2qFOJW-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  CMG President Shen Haixiong (L) and IOC President Thomas Bach jointly display a Paris 2024 No. 1 jersey. /CMG  President of the International Olympic Committee (IOC) Thomas Bach has expressed his gratitude to China Media Group (CMG) for its broadcast preparations for the upcoming Paris Summer Games.  He commended the significant support from the Chinese people and praised CMG's pivotal role, especially in the use of 8K Ultra HD technology and artificial intelligence, which he said had revolutionized the Olympic broadcasting.  President Bach also wished CMG great success in its coverage of the Games, and emphasized that the IOC will continue to deepen its comprehensive cooperation with CMG.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"